title: Ceasefire Negotiations
subtitle: The megacorps need a referee — we set the price
max-visits: 1
new-page: true
tags: event
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi = function() {
// --- reprisal knobs (edit here to rebalance demands) ---
// Leverage all three megacorps receive when negotiations open (accept if leverage > reprisal).
CABLE_NEG_LEVERAGE_BOOST = 5

// Police jurisdiction — reprisal on the corp that loses district security.
CABLE_NEG_REPR_VATS_SOYLENT = 2          // @take_vats_police
CABLE_NEG_REPR_RAILYARD_MAGRAIL = 2      // @take_railyard_police
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_SOYLENT = 1           // @take_docks_police (each belligerent)
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_MAGRAIL = 1
CABLE_NEG_REPR_LIMELIGHT_BRAZOS = 3      // @take_limelight_police (needs Vats/Railyard/Docks)

// Rival schadenfreude — reprisal lowered on corps that enjoy a rival's setback (always < gross raise).
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_VATS_MAGRAIL = 1        // Magrail likes Soylent losing Vats security
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_RAILYARD_SOYLENT = 1    // Soylent likes Magrail losing Railyard security
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_DOCKS_BRAZOS = 1        // Brazos likes both belligerents grumbling over Docks
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_SOYLENT = 1   // Belligerents like Brazos humiliated on Limelight
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_MAGRAIL = 1
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS = 1     // Brazos exempt / enjoys belligerents-only security tax
CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TRIALS_MIXED_BRAZOS = 1 // Brazos likes city–corp panel binding the fighters

// Police payroll — reprisal on each megacorp when city absorbs corp security wages.
CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH = 1           // @pay_city_2x
CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH = 2           // @pay_city_6x
CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH = 3     // @pay_city_6x_match (includes city police raise)
CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_SOYLENT = 1       // @pay_corp_10x (match corp payscale — asymmetric)
CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_MAGRAIL = 1
CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_BRAZOS = 2

// Security tax — reprisal on taxed corps (requires payroll demand first).
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_SOYLENT = 1   // @tax_half_belligerents
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_MAGRAIL = 1
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_SOYLENT = 2   // @tax_full_belligerents
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_MAGRAIL = 2
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_ALL_EACH = 1       // @tax_half_all_three
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_SOYLENT = 1    // @tax_full_all_three
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_MAGRAIL = 1
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_BRAZOS = 2

// Disband corp security — reprisal on each megacorp (incompatible with jurisdiction transfer).
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_SOYLENT = 3   // @disband_city_police
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_MAGRAIL = 3
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_BRAZOS = 2
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_SOYLENT = 2     // @disband_militia
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_MAGRAIL = 2
CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_BRAZOS = 1

// Civil rights — equal reprisal on all three (@demand_civil_rights).
CABLE_NEG_REPR_CIVIL_RIGHTS_EACH = 2

// Ceasefire trials — reprisal on corps that lose control of mercenary justice.
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_SOYLENT = 2   // @trials_city_judges
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_MAGRAIL = 2
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_BRAZOS = 1
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_SOYLENT = 1  // @trials_mixed_panel
CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_MAGRAIL = 1

// Judicial review — reprisal on all three (requires trial rules first).
CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_2_EACH = 1          // @review_2_city_3_corp
CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_4_EACH = 2          // @review_4_city_3_corp

// Infrastructure cap — reprisal on all three.
CABLE_NEG_REPR_INFRA_GENEROUS_EACH = 1   // @infra_cap_generous
CABLE_NEG_REPR_INFRA_FAIR_EACH = 2       // @infra_cap_fair

// Prior-leverage demands — reprisal on the targeted megacorp only.
CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_ENROLL_EACH = 1       // @demand_education_enroll_*
CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_PAY_EACH = 1          // @demand_education_pay_* (needs enrollment)
CABLE_NEG_REPR_LAND_TAX_EACH = 2         // @demand_land_tax_*

Q.cableNegLeverageBoost = CABLE_NEG_LEVERAGE_BOOST
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_VATS_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_VATS_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_RAILYARD_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_RAILYARD_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_LIMELIGHT_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_REPR_LIMELIGHT_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_VATS_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_VATS_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_RAILYARD_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_RAILYARD_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_DOCKS_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_DOCKS_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TRIALS_MIXED_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TRIALS_MIXED_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_ALL_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_ALL_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_CITY_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_REPR_DISBAND_MIL_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_CIVIL_RIGHTS_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_CIVIL_RIGHTS_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_BRAZOS = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_BRAZOS
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_SOYLENT = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_SOYLENT
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_MAGRAIL = CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_MAGRAIL
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_2_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_2_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_4_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_4_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_INFRA_GENEROUS_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_INFRA_GENEROUS_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_INFRA_FAIR_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_INFRA_FAIR_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_ENROLL_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_ENROLL_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_PAY_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_PAY_EACH
Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_LAND_TAX_EACH = CABLE_NEG_REPR_LAND_TAX_EACH
if (Q._cable_neg_api) return
Q._cable_neg_api = 1
Q.cableNegReprisalAdd = function(corp, delta) {
    Q[corp + '_reprisal'] = (Number(Q[corp + '_reprisal']) || 0) + delta
}
Q.cableNegReprisalAddEach = function(delta) {
    Q.cableNegReprisalAdd('soylent', delta)
    Q.cableNegReprisalAdd('magrail', delta)
    Q.cableNegReprisalAdd('brazos', delta)
}
Q.cableNegReprisalSub = function(corp, delta) {
    Q[corp + '_reprisal'] = Math.max(0, (Number(Q[corp + '_reprisal']) || 0) - delta)
}
Q.cableNegEffectiveRelief = function(downs, grossUp) {
    var i, grossDown = 0, out = []
    downs = downs || []
    if (grossUp < 2) { return out }
    for (i = 0; i < downs.length; i++) {
        if (downs[i].n > 0) { out.push({ corp: downs[i].corp, n: downs[i].n }) }
    }
    for (i = 0; i < out.length; i++) { grossDown += out[i].n }
    if (grossDown >= grossUp) {
        var budget = grossUp - 1
        for (i = 0; i < out.length; i++) {
            if (budget <= 0) { out[i].n = 0 }
            else if (out[i].n > budget) { out[i].n = budget; budget = 0 }
            else { budget -= out[i].n }
        }
    }
    return out
}
Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief = function(ups, downs) {
    var i, grossUp = 0
    ups = ups || []
    for (i = 0; i < ups.length; i++) { grossUp += ups[i].n }
    downs = Q.cableNegEffectiveRelief(downs, grossUp)
    for (i = 0; i < ups.length; i++) { Q.cableNegReprisalAdd(ups[i].corp, ups[i].n) }
    for (i = 0; i < downs.length; i++) {
        if (downs[i].n > 0) { Q.cableNegReprisalSub(downs[i].corp, downs[i].n) }
    }
}
Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief = function(ups, downs) {
    var i, grossUp = 0
    ups = ups || []
    for (i = 0; i < ups.length; i++) { grossUp += ups[i].n }
    downs = Q.cableNegEffectiveRelief(downs, grossUp)
    for (i = 0; i < ups.length; i++) { Q.cableNegReprisalSub(ups[i].corp, ups[i].n) }
    for (i = 0; i < downs.length; i++) {
        if (downs[i].n > 0) { Q.cableNegReprisalAdd(downs[i].corp, downs[i].n) }
    }
}
Q.cableNegApplyVatsPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [{ corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_VATS_SOYLENT }],
        [{ corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_VATS_MAGRAIL }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearVatsPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [{ corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_VATS_SOYLENT }],
        [{ corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_VATS_MAGRAIL }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegApplyRailyardPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [{ corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_RAILYARD_MAGRAIL }],
        [{ corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_RAILYARD_SOYLENT }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearRailyardPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [{ corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_RAILYARD_MAGRAIL }],
        [{ corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_RAILYARD_SOYLENT }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegApplyDocksPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_DOCKS_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearDocksPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_DOCKS_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_DOCKS_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegApplyLimelightPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_LIMELIGHT_BRAZOS }],
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_MAGRAIL }
        ]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearLimelightPolice = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_LIMELIGHT_BRAZOS }],
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_LIMELIGHT_MAGRAIL }
        ]
    )
}
Q.cableNegApplyTaxHalfBelligerents = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearTaxHalfBelligerents = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_BELL_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegApplyTaxFullBelligerents = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearTaxFullBelligerents = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_BELL_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TAX_BELL_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegApplyTrialsMixed = function() {
    Q.cableNegApplyWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TRIALS_MIXED_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearTrialsMixed = function() {
    Q.cableNegUndoWithRivalRelief(
        [
            { corp: 'soylent', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_SOYLENT },
            { corp: 'magrail', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_MIXED_MAGRAIL }
        ],
        [{ corp: 'brazos', n: Q.CABLE_NEG_RELIEF_TRIALS_MIXED_BRAZOS }]
    )
}
Q.cableNegClearCorpTax = function() {
    var t = Number(Q.cable_neg_corp_tax) || 0
    if (t === 1) { Q.cableNegClearTaxHalfBelligerents() }
    else if (t === 2) { Q.cableNegClearTaxFullBelligerents() }
    else if (t === 3) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_ALL_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_ALL_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_HALF_ALL_EACH)
    } else if (t === 4) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_SOYLENT)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_MAGRAIL)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TAX_FULL_ALL_BRAZOS)
    }
    Q.cable_neg_corp_tax = 0
    Q.cable_neg_corp_tax_fund = 0
    Q.cable_neg_brazos_tax_exempt = 0
}
Q.cableNegHasPoliceTransfer = function() {
    return Q.cable_neg_police_vats === 1 || Q.cable_neg_police_railyard === 1
        || Q.cable_neg_police_docks === 1 || Q.cable_neg_police_limelight === 1
}
Q.cableNegEffectivePolicePay = function() {
    var pay = Number(Q.cable_neg_police_pay) || 0
    if (pay > 0) { return pay }
    return Q.cableNegHasPoliceTransfer() ? 1 : 0
}
Q.cableNegApplyPolicePayReprisal = function(pay) {
    pay = Number(pay) || 0
    if (pay === 1) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalAddEach(Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH)
    } else if (pay === 2) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalAddEach(Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH)
    } else if (pay === 3) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalAddEach(Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH)
    } else if (pay === 4) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalAdd('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_SOYLENT)
        Q.cableNegReprisalAdd('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_MAGRAIL)
        Q.cableNegReprisalAdd('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_BRAZOS)
    }
}
Q.cableNegClearPolicePayReprisal = function(pay) {
    pay = Number(pay) || 0
    if (pay === 1) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_2X_EACH)
    } else if (pay === 2) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_EACH)
    } else if (pay === 3) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_6X_MATCH_EACH)
    } else if (pay === 4) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_SOYLENT)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_MAGRAIL)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_PAY_10X_BRAZOS)
    }
}
Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal = function() {
    var effective = Q.cableNegEffectivePolicePay()
    var applied = Number(Q.cable_neg_police_pay_applied) || 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_pay_effective = effective
    if (effective === applied) { return }
    if (applied > 0) { Q.cableNegClearPolicePayReprisal(applied) }
    if (effective > 0) { Q.cableNegApplyPolicePayReprisal(effective) }
    Q.cable_neg_police_pay_applied = effective
}
Q.cableNegClearPolicePay = function() {
    Q.cable_neg_police_pay = 0
    if ((Number(Q.cable_neg_corp_tax) || 0) > 0) { Q.cableNegClearCorpTax() }
    Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal()
}
Q.cableNegClearJudgeReview = function() {
    var j = Number(Q.cable_neg_judge_review) || 0
    if (j === 2) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_2_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_2_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_2_EACH)
    } else if (j === 4) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_4_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_4_EACH)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_JUDGE_4_EACH)
    }
    Q.cable_neg_judge_review = 0
}
Q.cableNegClearTrials = function() {
    if ((Number(Q.cable_neg_judge_review) || 0) > 0) { Q.cableNegClearJudgeReview() }
    var t = Number(Q.cable_neg_trials) || 0
    if (t === 1) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('soylent', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_SOYLENT)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('magrail', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_MAGRAIL)
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub('brazos', Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_TRIALS_CITY_BRAZOS)
    } else if (t === 2) {
        Q.cableNegClearTrialsMixed()
    }
    Q.cable_neg_trials = 0
}
Q.cableNegClearEducationPayCorp = function(corp) {
    if (Q['cable_neg_' + corp + '_education_pay'] === 1) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub(corp, Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_PAY_EACH)
        Q['cable_neg_' + corp + '_education_pay'] = 0
    }
}
Q.cableNegClearEducationEnrollCorp = function(corp) {
    Q.cableNegClearEducationPayCorp(corp)
    if (Q['cable_neg_' + corp + '_education_enroll'] === 1) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub(corp, Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_EDU_ENROLL_EACH)
        Q['cable_neg_' + corp + '_education_enroll'] = 0
    }
}
Q.cableNegClearLandTaxCorp = function(corp) {
    if (Q['cable_neg_' + corp + '_land_tax'] === 1) {
        Q.cableNegReprisalSub(corp, Q.CABLE_NEG_REPR_LAND_TAX_EACH)
        Q['cable_neg_' + corp + '_land_tax'] = 0
    }
}
Q.cableNegSyncCorpStances = function() {
    function stanceFor(corp) {
        var margin = (Number(Q[corp + '_leverage']) || 0) - (Number(Q[corp + '_reprisal']) || 0)
        var cat = 1
        if (margin > 3) { cat = 4 }
        else if (margin >= 2) { cat = 3 }
        else if (margin >= 1) { cat = 2 }
        Q['cable_neg_stance_' + corp] = cat
    }
    stanceFor('soylent')
    stanceFor('magrail')
    stanceFor('brazos')
}
}
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
if (Q.cable_neg_ready != 1) {
    Q.cable_neg_ready = 1
    Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost = Q.cableNegLeverageBoost
    Q.soylent_leverage = (Number(Q.soylent_leverage) || 0) + Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost
    Q.magrail_leverage = (Number(Q.magrail_leverage) || 0) + Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost
    Q.brazos_leverage = (Number(Q.brazos_leverage) || 0) + Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost

    Q.cable_neg_prior_soylent = (Number(Q.soylent_leverage) || 0) > Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost ? 1 : 0
    Q.cable_neg_prior_magrail = (Number(Q.magrail_leverage) || 0) > Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost ? 1 : 0
    Q.cable_neg_prior_brazos = (Number(Q.brazos_leverage) || 0) > Q.cable_neg_leverage_boost ? 1 : 0
    Q.cable_neg_prior_leverage = (
        Q.cable_neg_prior_soylent === 1
        || Q.cable_neg_prior_magrail === 1
        || Q.cable_neg_prior_brazos === 1
    ) ? 1 : 0

    Q.cable_neg_police_vats = 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_railyard = 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_docks = 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_limelight = 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_pay = 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_pay_applied = 0
    Q.cable_neg_police_pay_effective = 0
    Q.cable_neg_corp_tax = 0
    Q.cable_neg_corp_tax_fund = 0
    Q.cable_neg_brazos_tax_exempt = 0
    Q.cable_neg_civil_rights = 0
    Q.cable_neg_trials = 0
    Q.cable_neg_judge_review = 0
    Q.cable_neg_disband = 0
    Q.cable_neg_soylent_education_enroll = 0
    Q.cable_neg_magrail_education_enroll = 0
    Q.cable_neg_brazos_education_enroll = 0
    Q.cable_neg_soylent_education_pay = 0
    Q.cable_neg_magrail_education_pay = 0
    Q.cable_neg_brazos_education_pay = 0
    Q.cable_neg_soylent_land_tax = 0
    Q.cable_neg_magrail_land_tax = 0
    Q.cable_neg_brazos_land_tax = 0
    Q.cable_neg_infra_cap = 0
}
if (typeof Q.syncIgAttitudes === 'function') { Q.syncIgAttitudes() }
!}

The tether rupture left Community Soylent and Magrail Combine willing to talk — but only through us.  Brazos Zaibatsu sits at the table too, ostensibly as a neutral party but really as a party interested in screwing them both.  They need a neutral enforcer for the ceasefire; we need to decide what that costs them.

Leverage (after crisis boost): Soylent [+ soylent_leverage +] / reprisal [+ soylent_reprisal +]; Magrail [+ magrail_leverage +] / [+ magrail_reprisal +]; Brazos [+ brazos_leverage +] / [+ brazos_reprisal +].

Any package needs **two megacorps** to accept (leverage still above reprisal after our demands).  A third who refuses may strike back immediately if their reprisal exceeds their leverage.

- @terms_menu: Review and add demands
- @finalize_deal: Close the bargain

