If we absorb corporate security, someone pays them.  Without a separate demand, transferred police are assumed to stay on **city payscale (2× poverty)**.  Corporate scale is ruinous; higher city scales are merely expensive.

- @pay_city_2x: City payscale (2× poverty level)
- @pay_city_6x: City pays 6× poverty level
- @pay_city_6x_match: 6× poverty + raise city police to match
- @pay_corp_10x: Same payscale as corp security (10× poverty)
